title: #92Noon! 10a Hour - Rudy Balazhynets
description: Rudy is a pastor and soccer coach from Ukraine, in town with two of his youth teams for the USA Cup soccer tournament in Blaine. He paints a picture of what life in Ukraine is like during intense wartime, and the great respite for his kids here in Minnesota.
